sequenceDiagram
    participant ARGOCD as Argo CD
    participant API as kube-apiserver
    participant ADMISSION as Admission Webhooks<br/>(Kyverno / OPA)
    participant SCHEDULER as kube-scheduler
    participant KUBELET as kubelet (Node)
    participant CONTAINERD as containerd
    participant REGISTRY as OCI Registry

    ARGOCD->>API: Apply manifests (Deployment, Service, etc.)
    API->>ADMISSION: Mutating admission webhook
    ADMISSION-->>API: Mutate (inject sidecars, set defaults)
    API->>ADMISSION: Validating admission webhook
    ADMISSION-->>API: Validate (policy checks pass / block)
    API->>SCHEDULER: New Pod pending
    SCHEDULER-->>API: Bind Pod to Node (Karpenter may provision node)
    API->>KUBELET: Inform kubelet of scheduled Pod
    KUBELET->>REGISTRY: Pull image (verify Cosign signature)
    REGISTRY-->>KUBELET: Image layers
    KUBELET->>CONTAINERD: Create container
    CONTAINERD-->>KUBELET: Container running
    KUBELET-->>API: Pod status: Running
    API-->>ARGOCD: Resource health: Healthy
